description: [Status: stable] [Name: missing-format-string-key] [Message: Missing key %r in format string dictionary] Description: Used when a format string that uses named conversion specifiers is used with a dictionary that doesn't contain all the keys required by the format string. Problematic code: # +1: [missing-format-string-key] fruit_prices = """ Apple: %(apple_price)d 造 Orange: %(orange_price)d 造 """ % { "apple_price": 42 } Correct code: fruit_prices = """ Apple: %(apple_price)d 造 Orange: %(orange_price)d 造 """ % { "apple_price": 42, "orange_price": 87, } Created by the string checker.
